1. *Prednosti* ovog uređaja su visoka kvaliteta i dugotrajnost. (Advantages of this device are high quality and durability.)
2. Moguće je iskoristiti *prednosti* tehnologije i u drugim industrijama. (It is possible to utilize the advantages of technology in other industries.)
3. Tim je iskoristio svoje *prednosti* kako bi pobijedio u utakmici. (The team used their advantages to win the game.)
4. Naša tvrtka nudi *prednosti* poput fleksibilnog radnog vremena i bonusa za uspjeh. (Our company offers benefits such as flexible working hours and performance bonuses.)
5. Želimo izvući *prednosti* iz ovog poslovnog dogovora. (We want to reap the benefits from this business deal.)
6. Osiguravanje sigurnosti kupaca je *prednost* koju naša tvrtka uvijek ima na umu. (Ensuring customer safety is an advantage that our company always keeps in mind.)
7. Ako želite ostvariti *prednost* na tržištu, morate biti inovativni. (If you want to gain an advantage in the market, you must be innovative.)
8. *Prednostima* ovog proizvoda može se pristupiti na našoj web stranici. (The advantages of this product can be accessed on our website.)
9. Iako postoje *prednosti* ovog rješenja, postoje i neke nedostatke. (Although there are advantages to this solution, there are also some drawbacks.)
10. Kompanija je pronašla *prednosti* u outsourcingu određenih poslovnih funkcija. (The company found advantages in outsourcing certain business functions.)